.SH OPTION USAGE
.\" --------------------------------------------------------------------
.
There are no other options than
.BR \-h ,
.BR \-\-help ,
.BR \-v ,
and
.BR \%\-\-version ;
these options provoke the printing of a version or usage information,
respectively, and all
.I filespec
